	(text "Calcumaker 16 — Display (MULTI-CHANNEL). Row1/2/3 are three instances of ONE reusable sheet (display_row.kicad_sch). Shared bus is carried on global nets +5V / GND / DISP_CLK; each row's serial data DIN is a hierarchical pin fed by DIN1/DIN2/DIN3 from the interconnect. Top row (Row3 / U3 / DS33-48) is optional -> 2- or 3-row build."
